people, and He has given horrible names to

00:52:46.889 --> 00:52:54.839
them, who try to oppress the people, who try
to devour the people and He calls that the

00:52:54.839 --> 00:53:00.429
religion now has become the compromise between
the two.

00:53:00.429 --> 00:53:07.629
While the innocent suffer, while the simple
suffer, while the seekers suffer, while the

00:53:07.629 --> 00:53:10.569
good suffer, that's the fact.

00:53:10.569 --> 00:53:16.808
Let us all of us join together now and get
our realization.

00:53:16.808 --> 00:53:18.379
Become the spirit.

00:53:18.379 --> 00:53:23.558
Is the easiest thing to do for you, because
the Holy Ghost, which is the Kundalini, is

00:53:23.558 --> 00:53:24.699
within you.

00:53:24.699 --> 00:53:29.978
In the triangular bone She resides and She
can be awakened.

00:53:29.978 --> 00:53:35.988
Now one may say that, "Why didn't He talk
about Kundalini?

00:53:35.988 --> 00:53:39.669
Whatever He talked, who listened to him?

00:53:39.669 --> 00:53:43.659
Whatever He said, who tried to understand;
till today I don't find many people have understood

00:53:43.659 --> 00:53:45.469
Him.

00:53:45.469 --> 00:53:51.319
Whatever He manifested, who bothered to know
about it?

00:53:51.319 --> 00:53:55.968
And if He had talked of something more, it
would have been obscure.

00:53:55.968 --> 00:54:03.468
But He says, "I don't care for the idiots
for whom My sayings are obscure."

00:54:03.468 --> 00:54:04.468
He says clearly.

00:54:04.468 --> 00:54:12.359
He has used only thrice the word 'idiot' I
think, many times 'stupid' and so many times

00:54:12.359 --> 00:54:13.679
'the fools'.

00:54:13.679 --> 00:54:21.159
Above all that, to Me, all of them are God's
own children.

00:54:21.159 --> 00:54:23.599
I know how He was angry.

00:54:23.599 --> 00:54:32.438
I know why He was angry and I also understand
Him that He thought that, before Sahaja Yoga

00:54:32.438 --> 00:54:41.139
coming here, let Me scold them, let Me give
them a thump, let Me open them with a big

00:54:41.139 --> 00:54:43.438
blow, so they are ready.

00:54:43.438 --> 00:54:50.419
But in His criticism, I read, they said He
was not acceptable because He went too far.

00:54:50.419 --> 00:54:52.429
Same with Me.

00:54:52.429 --> 00:54:54.438
People don't accept Me because I go too far.

00:54:54.438 --> 00:54:55.719
I must try to please them.

00:54:55.719 --> 00:54:58.859
Am I seeking your votes that I should try
to please you?

00:54:58.859 --> 00:55:03.989
I have to tell you the truth, whether you
like it or not.

00:55:03.989 --> 00:55:08.569
I want you to accept it because that's what
I am here for.

00:55:08.569 --> 00:55:12.268
I'm here for that, that you accept the truth
and get it.

00:55:12.268 --> 00:55:13.548
I'll do my level best.

00:55:13.548 --> 00:55:18.489
I can make food for you, I can give you good
food to you, I can give you presents, I can

00:55:18.489 --> 00:55:21.458
do whatever a Mother can do for Her children.

00:55:21.458 --> 00:55:29.788
But when it doesn't work out, She has to shout
sometimes.

00:55:29.788 --> 00:55:35.609
She has to say things clearly, because you
have to get it.

00:55:35.609 --> 00:55:39.899
Now you cannot force it on people, this is
the biggest problem is.

00:55:39.899 --> 00:55:46.929
You cannot force Self-realization on to people,
you cannot do it by force.

00:55:46.929 --> 00:55:50.778
Say if the ... supposing Russians tell Me
they are very much interested to know about

00:55:50.778 --> 00:55:51.778
Sahaja Yoga.

00:55:51.778 --> 00:55:52.778
No doubt.

00:55:52.778 --> 00:55:59.528
But if they tell Me that, "You come to our
government and give them realization", I cannot,

00:55:59.528 --> 00:56:01.619
I cannot do it.

00:56:01.619 --> 00:56:02.919
You have to be free people.

00:56:02.919 --> 00:56:10.988
When you are free, then you are abandoned,
see, the wages of freedom we are paying.

00:56:10.988 --> 00:56:15.778
Nobody is free, in New York if you go, I have
to take out all these ornaments, which I am

00:56:15.778 --> 00:56:18.288
supposed to wear because of My family.

00:56:18.288 --> 00:56:24.829
I have to go there without a purse, I have
to tie up my purse inside here see something,

00:56:24.829 --> 00:56:28.429
otherwise they'll rob it.

00:56:28.429 --> 00:56:31.129
Nothing is safe.

00:56:31.129 --> 00:56:36.829
So this kind of a freedom which leads to violence,
to butchery; actually the way we have butchered

00:56:36.829 --> 00:56:43.339
our children, butchered our elders, the way
insulted every one of them, all that goes

00:56:43.339 --> 00:56:45.069
hand in hand with freedom.

00:56:45.069 --> 00:56:51.349
This is no freedom, this is absolutely unleashed
abandonment of the brutal self within us.

00:56:51.349 --> 00:56:59.699
So whether you go to Russia or to here Sahaja
Yoga is in a problem, whether you go to the

00:56:59.699 --> 00:57:09.159
left or to the right, I just don't understand,
where will it prosper, where freedom is used

00:57:09.159 --> 00:57:12.718
with wisdom, with respect.

00:57:12.718 --> 00:57:19.788
If you cannot respect the freedom of others
you do not have the freedom at all, you have

00:57:19.788 --> 00:57:23.629
never known the freedom, you have never enjoyed
the freedom.

00:57:23.629 --> 00:57:32.968
So the freedom of human beings has to be respected
and when this freedom is respected, then only

00:57:32.968 --> 00:57:40.069
you can get your realization and then only
you can enter into higher freedom, into complete

00:57:40.069 --> 00:57:44.669
liberty that Blake has described.

00:57:44.669 --> 00:57:54.548
There are seekers, so many seekers in this
country, and so many are lost, so many are

00:57:54.548 --> 00:57:55.859
lost.

00:57:55.859 --> 00:58:03.659
There have been people who are saved by Sahaja
Yoga, who have been taking drugs, overnight

00:58:03.659 --> 00:58:05.359
they gave up, overnight.

00:58:05.359 --> 00:58:06.359
How?

00:58:06.359 --> 00:58:12.169
It's a mechanism within you, God has built
that, that power of the spirit when it enlightens

00:58:12.169 --> 00:58:15.339
you, you just become so powerful, you give
up.

00:58:15.339 --> 00:58:19.708
But beforehand if I say, "Don't have this
and don't have that", you cannot do it.

00:58:19.708 --> 00:58:23.438
You do not have that power of the spirit.

00:58:23.438 --> 00:58:29.489
Most of the incarnations who came before Christ
didn't realize this point, that human beings

00:58:29.489 --> 00:58:33.508
are not enlightened, they don't have the power
of the spirit within them.

00:58:33.508 --> 00:58:37.758
Christ realized it and He said it openly,
"You are to be born again."

00:58:37.758 --> 00:58:44.548
Not only that, but He said, "First of all
forgive, talk of forgiveness."

00:58:44.548 --> 00:58:50.329
So that they settle down, that they are not
paranoid, that they are not upset.

00:58:50.329 --> 00:58:56.639
Let them be settled down in peace and in compassion
and then awaken their kundalini and then give

00:58:56.639 --> 00:58:57.718
them realization.

00:58:57.718 --> 00:59:02.819
So then you have the power, then there is
no temptation, nothing like that.

00:59:02.819 --> 00:59:05.449
Will you tempt Christ with anything?

00:59:05.449 --> 00:59:06.708
You cannot.

00:59:06.708 --> 00:59:10.909
In the same way you do not get enslaved to
any temptations.

00:59:10.909 --> 00:59:17.139
You rise in your own beauty and glory, and
your own strength and power.

00:59:17.139 --> 00:59:21.258
You don't have to get subdued to anything.

00:59:21.258 --> 00:59:24.958
This is what is Self-realization.

00:59:24.958 --> 00:59:29.169
Sahaja Yoga came to London about twelve years
back when I came.

00:59:29.169 --> 00:59:33.109
Now I am not an immigrant for your information,
at all.

00:59:33.109 --> 00:59:40.349
I just came by chance, I should say, or by
God's ordained programming.

00:59:40.349 --> 00:59:46.349
My husband got elected to this job out of
hundred and thirty-four nations, you see.

00:59:46.349 --> 00:59:51.278
He was elected , we came here, just because
he was elected, not even appointed, but elected,

00:59:51.278 --> 00:59:53.028
and elected four times unanimously.

00:59:53.028 --> 00:59:56.989
He is the senior most senior secretary-general.

00:59:56.989 --> 01:00:04.448
So we had to come here, and that's how I'm
here, otherwise I may not have ever come to

01:00:04.448 --> 01:00:08.579
England to teach Sahaja Yoga.

01:00:08.579 --> 01:00:18.308
With Blake, One feels compelled to try and
try and try to establish Jerusalem, whatever

01:00:18.308 --> 01:00:27.349
may be the case, whatever may be the disappointment,
whatever may be the disgust, doesn't matter.

01:00:27.349 --> 01:00:29.909
One has to do it.

01:00:29.909 --> 01:00:37.709
He had such faith in the England's soil that
we have to build the Jerusalem.

01:00:37.709 --> 01:00:46.548
But first, everyone of you who are here must
get your realization and humble down before

01:00:46.548 --> 01:00:47.548
your realization.

01:00:47.548 --> 01:00:51.319
You are not to be arrogant with it.

01:00:51.319 --> 01:00:58.663
He said Christ was not humble before human
beings, but before God He was.

01:00:58.663 --> 01:00:59.939
Before His Father He was.

01:00:59.939 --> 01:01:06.458
In the same way, you have to be humble before
your spirit and before your Self-realization

01:01:06.458 --> 01:01:12.988
and you have to get to the higher state.

01:01:12.988 --> 01:01:16.949
It's surprising that in India, we had all
this knowledge all these years, but we were

01:01:16.949 --> 01:01:20.478
supposed to be heathens, I don't know what
else they called us.

01:01:20.478 --> 01:01:22.978
We were supposed to be slaves.

01:01:22.978 --> 01:01:28.079
Nobody wanted to know anything about it, the
knowledge of the roots existed and our intellectuals

01:01:28.079 --> 01:01:33.399
also never bothered, they always followed
Oxford and Cambridge traditions.

01:01:33.399 --> 01:01:42.718
With this Oxbridge business, we never got
through people to tell them about this great

01:01:42.718 --> 01:01:46.819
knowledge we had in that country and everything
subsided.

01:01:46.819 --> 01:01:51.599
This knowledge is not meant for India, is
not meant for any particular place, is meant

01:01:51.599 --> 01:01:56.619
for the whole world, as your knowledge of
science, all the knowledge of the tree is

01:01:56.619 --> 01:02:00.698
meant for the whole world, which you gave
it to us, or to give it to all the eastern

01:02:00.698 --> 01:02:02.469
countries and people accept it.

01:02:02.469 --> 01:02:08.359
What's the harm in accepting the knowledge
which comes to you for your benevolence; only

01:02:08.359 --> 01:02:14.379
because it is from the eastern side you feel
so insecure about it?

01:02:14.379 --> 01:02:17.879
From where did Christ come?

01:02:17.879 --> 01:02:20.678
He came from America?

01:02:20.678 --> 01:02:23.268
I think He must have run away.

01:02:23.268 --> 01:02:34.879
Despite that I must say among all of them,
British are the most matured.

01:02:34.879 --> 01:02:40.459
But we run after Americans, we run after French,
we run after everyone, not being aware of

01:02:40.459 --> 01:02:46.808
ourselves, what we are, we are wisdom.

01:02:46.808 --> 01:02:56.278
We are the people who represent the heart
of the universe and time has taken, from Him

01:02:56.278 --> 01:02:58.599
to this time, that we have matured now.

01:02:58.599 --> 01:03:06.729
I hope we have matured enough to understand
that there has to be a breakthrough.

01:03:06.729 --> 01:03:14.819
When they published My handbills, you see,
somehow it so happened that My face has come

01:03:14.819 --> 01:03:16.079
out quite black in that.

01:03:16.079 --> 01:03:22.739
I said, "Forget it, nobody will come to our
program, if you show such a black face they'll

01:03:22.739 --> 01:03:29.758
say, 'oh, somebody coming from Africa is trying
to teach us what is Jerusalem'."

01:03:29.758 --> 01:03:34.058
So they had to re-do it, to show that I am
not that black.

01:03:34.058 --> 01:03:43.409
What difference does it make, the skin deep
color?

01:03:43.409 --> 01:03:51.028
The color comes from the heart, the beauty
comes from the heart, the exuberance of the

01:03:51.028 --> 01:03:59.579
heart expresses that beauty on your being
and the beauty of the truth is that, that

01:03:59.579 --> 01:04:02.119
it acts, it works.

01:04:02.119 --> 01:04:07.448
It just doesn't decorate itself, it doesn't
try to take to ways and methods of luring

01:04:07.448 --> 01:04:12.899
people but it acts, whether you like it or
not it acts.

01:04:12.899 --> 01:04:16.458
Let us work it out.

01:04:16.458 --> 01:04:18.579
Is simple.

01:04:18.579 --> 01:04:26.409
Instead of going into intellectual feats and
going into the direction of finite understanding

01:04:26.409 --> 01:04:32.958
through your brains, let us go to the infinite;
that's only possible when you get to your

01:04:32.958 --> 01:04:37.198
spirit, which is infinite, which creates the
collective consciousness within.

01:04:37.198 --> 01:04:43.298
Which creates, I say, which means knowledge,
but knowledge does not mean what you know

01:04:43.298 --> 01:04:48.968
through your brain, but what you know through
your central nervous system; that you can

01:04:48.968 --> 01:04:53.958
feel it, that you can feel the chakras of
everyone on your fingertips.

01:04:53.958 --> 01:04:58.879
Mohammed Sahib has said, "At the time of resurrection
your hands will speak".

01:04:58.879 --> 01:05:04.268
But look at the Muslims, they never, never
talk of the resurrection, when most of Koran

01:05:04.268 --> 01:05:05.659
is nothing but resurrection.

01:05:05.659 --> 01:05:09.248
They talk of the doomsday because they have
to make money by frightening people.

01:05:09.248 --> 01:05:13.728
Beware of the doomsday, you give the money,
we'll save you, we'll give a certificate;

01:05:13.728 --> 01:05:16.558
at the doomsday you stand with the certificate,
you'll be saved.

01:05:16.558 --> 01:05:19.458
First they will go down in the doomsday.

01:05:19.458 --> 01:05:33.978
This is for every religion, people have used
it for very baser things, making money, creating

01:05:33.978 --> 01:05:37.149
political ideas.

01:05:37.149 --> 01:05:46.058
I can't understand how can diamonds be thrown
into dirt like this, and covered with that,

01:05:46.058 --> 01:05:49.758
and the fragrance turned into filth.

01:05:49.758 --> 01:05:52.518
It is beyond Me.

01:05:52.518 --> 01:05:59.079
The powers of human beings sometimes supercede
that of God, you can see the way they can

01:05:59.079 --> 01:06:04.659
change the forms, they change the beauty,
change everything that is reality, into something

01:06:04.659 --> 01:06:06.798
nonsensical and stupid.

01:06:06.798 --> 01:06:11.558
And they live with it, they don't want to
know about it; they enjoy it.

01:06:11.558 --> 01:06:15.119
"We are very happy people, what's wrong."

01:06:15.144 --> 01:06:19.425
What a waste, one feels, of this creation.

01:06:19.450 --> 01:06:29.439
One feels with what aspirations and visions
these human beings were created on this earth.

01:06:29.439 --> 01:06:39.509
And then what should we do to make them understand
what they are, to make them aware with that

01:06:39.509 --> 01:06:45.949
perception, with that vision of the Divine
that they are?

01:06:45.998 --> 01:06:55.008
Sometimes, I also cry in the wilderness and
share some of the pathos of all these poets

01:06:55.008 --> 01:07:03.359
who came on this earth and suffered, and suffered,
and suffered.

01:07:03.359 --> 01:07:11.478
I hope today, with all this anguish, whatever
I am telling you, you will try to see that

01:07:11.478 --> 01:07:15.859
sincerity is the only way you can understand
yourself.

01:07:15.859 --> 01:07:24.069
No books , nothing, no conditioning, no denial,
nothing can convince you but the sincerity

01:07:24.069 --> 01:07:33.728
to know the spirit, which is within you and
this sincerity I call it as the pure desire.

01:07:33.728 --> 01:07:39.728
If you have that pure desire, which is the
power of your kundalini, you will get your

01:07:39.728 --> 01:07:41.068
realization.

01:07:41.093 --> 01:07:44.537
Now, just now, the shoot.

01:07:45.092 --> 01:07:50.558
That's all is needed, the pure desire to be
the Spirit, nothing more than that.

01:07:50.558 --> 01:07:58.649
But when it is awakened, then it is to be
looked after, that's very important; it has

01:07:58.649 --> 01:08:06.798
to be looked after, it has to be kept burning,
it has to be maneuvered and kept at a point

01:08:06.798 --> 01:08:10.538
that you start growing more and more.

01:08:10.538 --> 01:08:15.188
I need not tell you all about Sahaja Yoga,
it's going to be too much for you, but how

01:08:15.188 --> 01:08:19.359
Blake has worked for us.

01:08:19.359 --> 01:08:28.129
So many poets have done this job and now the
new great poets are coming to finish us off,

01:08:28.129 --> 01:08:41.808
to please the media, to make money, befool
us, using flowery words, pleasing sentences,

01:08:41.808 --> 01:08:45.064
taking us to hell directly.

01:08:45.120 --> 01:08:50.899
Beware of them, beware, save your children
from them, save the whole community.

01:08:50.899 --> 01:08:56.680
The whole of England has to be saved because
if the heart dies, the whole universe will

01:08:56.705 --> 01:08:58.006
die.

01:08:58.839 --> 01:09:05.538
May God bless you.

01:09:27.849 --> 01:09:43.704
The Sahaja yogis didn't want Me to allow you
to ask Me questions but I think better ask

01:09:43.737 --> 01:09:45.177
Me some questions.

01:09:45.177 --> 01:09:48.276
Q.....about the chakras....

01:09:48.276 --> 01:09:52.417
Shri Mataji: Yes sir.

01:09:52.417 --> 01:09:57.286
That's what I said, that I didn't talk about
them because it would be too long a lecture

01:09:57.286 --> 01:10:04.068
but we have got a book on this, a little book
and there it is all written though I say that

01:10:04.068 --> 01:10:11.306
before realization don't even read that book,
can create problems.

01:10:11.306 --> 01:10:18.213
You can know all about the subtle side, the
chakras and everything without paying anything,

01:10:18.242 --> 01:10:19.732
without any effort.

01:10:20.348 --> 01:10:25.887
There are people now in England, you will
be surprised, so many of them are excellent

01:10:25.887 --> 01:10:30.717
Sahaja yogis who are experts and they will
tell you all about it very clearly.

01:10:30.717 --> 01:10:32.556
We have got books to explain.

01:10:32.556 --> 01:10:34.976
As you see there are seven chakras are shown
here.

01:10:34.976 --> 01:10:40.870
The lowermost is the Mooladhara Chakra, is
the innocence.

01:10:41.497 --> 01:10:46.627
Q:...can you see it with your eyes, outside
the body, can you see it?

01:10:46.627 --> 01:10:52.476
Shri Mataji: If you see something then you
are not that.

01:10:52.476 --> 01:10:57.506
And people have seen it because they were
not that, because they moved on the sides,

01:10:57.506 --> 01:11:01.197
on the sympathetic nervous system, what we
call the Ida and Pingala.

01:11:01.197 --> 01:11:05.687
When you go on sympathetic nervous system
you can see it from outside.

01:11:05.687 --> 01:11:10.267
Like this building you can see it from outside,
but when you are in it you don't see it, you

01:11:10.267 --> 01:11:11.776
see only the inside.

01:11:11.776 --> 01:11:18.076
So that's what it is, when you ascend, you
need not see anything, you become, you get

01:11:18.076 --> 01:11:23.467
the powers.

01:11:23.467 --> 01:11:29.596
People have seen it no doubt, but that one
should not ask for.

01:11:29.596 --> 01:11:40.796
I can see the glass - better to drink the
water.

01:11:40.796 --> 01:11:42.006
Now what else?

01:11:42.006 --> 01:11:51.716
Q:....what do You do with all Your wealth,
all your money?

01:11:51.716 --> 01:11:54.616
Shri Mataji: My money?

01:11:54.616 --> 01:12:01.627
Are you from the bank?

01:12:01.627 --> 01:12:06.957
What I do with My money - what do you want
Me to do?

01:12:06.957 --> 01:12:09.076
What sort of a question is this?

01:12:09.076 --> 01:12:17.167
Ask a simple straightforward question madam
I don't understand what do I do with My money,

01:12:17.167 --> 01:12:19.197
I don't do anything with it.

01:12:19.197 --> 01:12:24.407
Actually My husband manages his money, I ask
him whatever I like.

01:12:24.407 --> 01:12:28.207
Of course he earns a lot no doubt, he earns
very much.

01:12:28.207 --> 01:12:32.316
I sometimes tell him, "I'm ashamed the way
they give you money," because he doesn't even

01:12:32.316 --> 01:12:33.816
pay any tax you know.

01:12:33.816 --> 01:12:38.207
Of course I do spend some money on Sahaja
Yoga, I must confess I have to sometimes,

01:12:38.207 --> 01:12:39.276
what to do?

01:12:39.276 --> 01:12:47.336
One has to and these people have their own
ashrams, where they stay, and look after it.

01:12:47.336 --> 01:12:50.937
For this hall they must have collected some
money I don't know, I don't know what do they

01:12:50.937 --> 01:12:53.957
do with their money, I don't know, I have
no idea, I've never seen that.

01:12:53.957 --> 01:12:56.846
They are honest people, they all know all
about it.

01:12:56.846 --> 01:13:02.596
I don't know anything, I have nothing to do
with it.

01:13:02.596 --> 01:13:09.086
This is the aggressiveness, "What do I do
with My money" Just look at this.

01:13:09.086 --> 01:13:11.147
Yes sir?

01:13:11.147 --> 01:13:25.296
Q....a man has mental illness, he wants to
know whether he'll have it after he dies....

01:13:39.434 --> 01:13:45.577
Shri Mataji: No, no, no, just now you can
cure it.

01:13:45.602 --> 01:13:47.441
Why to think of death?

01:13:47.466 --> 01:13:53.479
You can be cured of your mental illness at
least, minimum, that could be done.

01:13:53.504 --> 01:14:04.036
Q....How can you tell that it's Self-realization?

01:14:04.036 --> 01:14:06.296
You feel a breeze but how does it become...

01:14:20.452 --> 01:14:24.692
Shri Mataji: You see, when you feel the cool
breeze is the beginning of it, all right?

01:14:24.717 --> 01:14:28.382
Now you have to see what this cool breeze
is, all right?

01:14:28.407 --> 01:14:34.407
Now if you go to a college of science or a
college of medicine what you have to do is

01:14:34.432 --> 01:14:41.893
to see what it is, isn't it; and to see whatever
it says does it prove.

01:14:41.893 --> 01:14:49.412
Now, when you see the cool breeze in your
hand, what happens that it is, as I said,

01:14:49.412 --> 01:14:53.976
is the compassion of God say for example,
you just believe in the hypothesis just now.

01:14:54.001 --> 01:14:58.567
Now what is this compassion doing, is made
you a computer.

01:14:58.592 --> 01:15:05.052
On the fingertips you can tell what centers
are catching, of yours and of others, so you

01:15:05.077 --> 01:15:07.306
become the diagnosis.

01:15:07.331 --> 01:15:14.982
Now if you know a little few gestures by which
you can handle this power, you can cure them.

01:15:15.007 --> 01:15:17.513
That's the minimum, all right?

01:15:17.538 --> 01:15:22.169
You can know from this whether you have mental
problem or you have emotional problem, or

01:15:22.194 --> 01:15:25.623
you have physical problem and of what nature.

01:15:26.071 --> 01:15:30.605
This is how is the self-knowledge starts,
from the very basics.

01:15:30.630 --> 01:15:35.229
What's your problem with you, first let us
see the problem on the centers, all right?

01:15:35.254 --> 01:15:40.405
Then you move forward when you go with it,
then you understand what's the problem with

01:15:40.430 --> 01:15:45.559
others; then what's the problem in the collective;
then what's the problem of this country; and

01:15:45.736 --> 01:15:52.766
if you know how to solve them, sitting down
here, you can do it, you can solve it.

01:15:52.791 --> 01:15:57.872
But this is the breeze which has to be felt
first because this is the breeze which we

01:15:57.897 --> 01:16:01.806
call as the all-pervading power of God.

01:16:01.882 --> 01:16:07.943
Now, just because I say you should not believe
Me, because blind faith is of no use, but

01:16:07.943 --> 01:16:11.483
you can experiment and see for yourself.

01:16:11.483 --> 01:16:13.283
Even little children know.

01:16:13.283 --> 01:16:16.862
They can tell you what is catching in you,
what chakras are catching.

01:16:16.862 --> 01:16:22.243
You can have ten children, 'fold' their eyes,
put them before a gentleman, immediately they'll

01:16:22.243 --> 01:16:24.683
raise this finger or this finger.

01:16:24.683 --> 01:16:29.592
Supposing they raise this finger, means this
person feels terribly guilty.

01:16:29.592 --> 01:16:34.703
He must be a Catholic that he feels so guilty.

01:16:34.703 --> 01:16:38.843
That the children won't say but you will know
that this is the chakra is caught up here

01:16:38.843 --> 01:16:41.933
because he's feeling guilty.

01:16:41.933 --> 01:16:47.922
Like that you can go on finding on your own
being like a laboratory the whole thing becomes

01:16:47.922 --> 01:16:55.003
like a computer because it is knowledge, knowledge
through your central nervous system, through

01:16:55.003 --> 01:16:57.922
your evolutionary process.

01:16:57.922 --> 01:17:02.142
But you have to practice and understand what
it is.

01:17:02.142 --> 01:17:07.062
If I give you a car, how will you know it
moves unless and until you get into it and

01:17:07.062 --> 01:17:09.783
know how to drive it, isn't it.

01:17:09.783 --> 01:17:17.062
You have to give some time, not much, but
you enjoy, best part of it you enjoy doing

01:17:17.062 --> 01:17:18.062
the whole thing.

01:17:18.062 --> 01:17:25.092
It just flows automatically, you don't have
to do anything about it.

01:17:25.092 --> 01:17:31.943
But one has to learn, little bit, what it
is.

01:17:31.943 --> 01:17:38.533
Before realization you don't have to do anything,
it just forms spontaneously as the seed is

01:17:38.533 --> 01:17:40.683
sown in the Mother Earth, all right?

01:17:40.683 --> 01:17:45.772
Then when it comes out, then you have to look
after it; the same way you have to look after

01:17:45.772 --> 01:17:47.802
your realization, respect it.

01:17:47.802 --> 01:17:49.642
Then you become the masters.

01:17:49.642 --> 01:17:55.152
We have one master standing here and we have
so many.

01:17:55.152 --> 01:18:04.415
They are just like you to look at, but they
know so much and they are so humble.

01:18:04.415 --> 01:18:09.852
They don't go about with a big plate on their
heads "I am the master of this and master

01:18:09.852 --> 01:18:10.852
of that" nothing.

01:18:10.852 --> 01:18:16.713
They are doing all their jobs, they are doing
very well, they are blessed and also they

01:18:16.713 --> 01:18:21.253
are helping people to get their realization.

01:18:21.253 --> 01:18:26.373
You'll be surprised in Sahaja Yoga very difficult
to get an unemployed person.

01:18:26.373 --> 01:18:28.083
All of them are employed.

01:18:28.083 --> 01:18:32.073
If they are unemployed they get employment
with God also.

01:18:34.653 --> 01:18:37.043
Basically they are employed by God.

01:18:38.035 --> 01:18:39.035
All right?

01:18:39.567 --> 01:18:47.210
Q... is this the only way to get realization?

01:18:47.235 --> 01:18:51.221
Shri Mataji: Yes, of course; there cannot
be another, God could not make thousand and

01:18:51.246 --> 01:18:52.945
one, could He?

01:18:52.970 --> 01:18:58.211
That would be too much of a headache , like
as you sprout the seed, how do you do it?

01:18:58.236 --> 01:18:59.236
Spontaneously.

01:18:59.261 --> 01:19:04.531
Sahaja Yoga means spontaneous, living process
is always spontaneous.

01:19:04.715 --> 01:19:09.945
Now supposing we want to sprout a seed and
we take out the primule, push it out and push

01:19:09.970 --> 01:19:13.430
it inside the Mother Earth, will it sprout
- no.

01:19:13.455 --> 01:19:17.886
You have to take advantage of the powers of
the Mother Earth, to sprout a seed, isn't

01:19:17.911 --> 01:19:20.091
it?

01:19:25.723 --> 01:19:36.252
Q. ...saying she has not come across Sahaja
Yoga in the religions, that there are many

01:19:36.277 --> 01:19:36.874
religions.

01:19:37.181 --> 01:19:40.508
Shri Mataji: In the religions there's no ... religions
are no religions, that's the trouble is.

01:19:40.545 --> 01:19:44.965
I have told you all this just now that there
is nothing, they will never mention that is

01:19:44.990 --> 01:19:46.630
sensible, but it's not so.

01:19:46.687 --> 01:19:52.437
I would say Sikhism, we can say is the latest
religion.

01:19:52.437 --> 01:19:59.417
I mean there are so many verses about, much
later than Islam, Sikhism came on this earth

01:19:59.417 --> 01:20:04.417
and they have said that, complete description,
I mean you don't understand Hindi otherwise

01:20:04.417 --> 01:20:09.497
I would have told you - Ida, Pingala, Sushumna
- everything they have described - Kabira

01:20:09.497 --> 01:20:15.467
has described at such length that we have
in India a great poet Gyaneshwara and He has

01:20:15.467 --> 01:20:17.487
described all about kundalini.

01:20:17.487 --> 01:20:21.107
If you go in Maharashtra and tell them that
somebody is going to awaken the kundalini,

01:20:21.107 --> 01:20:26.647
they'll all rush, they know all about it.

01:20:26.647 --> 01:20:29.107
How many years did Christ live?

01:20:29.107 --> 01:20:33.997
How many times He could talk to people?

01:20:33.997 --> 01:20:38.997
How many of them accepted Him and how many
of them understood Him?

01:20:38.997 --> 01:20:49.212
He went to a wrong place, I tell you; all
were deaf, dumb and brainless.

01:20:49.848 --> 01:20:52.878
How will they understand?

01:20:52.903 --> 01:20:57.513
How could He talk about Kundalini when everybody
was after His life?

01:20:57.513 --> 01:21:02.741
But He did talk of Holy Ghost, He talked of
the Comforter He was going to send.

01:21:02.766 --> 01:21:05.806
He talked of so many things in that short
time.

01:21:05.831 --> 01:21:11.871
Do you know for four years I was struggling
with seven hippies in London; for four years.

01:21:11.896 --> 01:21:19.196
I must say, it's very creditable for Him in
three and a half years to talk so much.

01:21:19.221 --> 01:21:23.591
How many years Blake had to work hard to talk
to you?

01:21:23.616 --> 01:21:25.856
Is it easy to talk to people about truth?

01:21:25.881 --> 01:21:30.951
Very difficult; everybody is extremely intelligent
and wise, nobody want to listen to anything,

01:21:30.976 --> 01:21:31.976
do they?

01:21:32.829 --> 01:21:38.930
But in India we have a tradition; we know
it; that you have to ascend.

01:21:38.955 --> 01:21:41.197
The whole thing works out that way.

01:21:41.222 --> 01:21:46.162
If they talk of kundalini, not in the North
so much, but in Maharashtra, if you go, if

01:21:46.187 --> 01:21:49.551
you go in the South, you'll be amazed six
thousand people, seven thousand people come

01:21:49.576 --> 01:21:50.576
in a village.

01:21:50.601 --> 01:21:54.231
They have seen it, these people have seen
it, they come in bullock carts, they come

01:21:54.256 --> 01:22:03.066
in, any way that is possible for them, buses,
and trains, and they walk miles together when

01:22:03.091 --> 01:22:05.721
they hear I'm there.

01:22:05.746 --> 01:22:12.812
Once I was coming from a program in the night
and suddenly I found lots of people lying

01:22:12.837 --> 01:22:13.837
on the road.

01:22:14.060 --> 01:22:15.684
I said, "Who are these people?"

01:22:15.709 --> 01:22:18.278
They said, "Mother we couldn't reach Your
program, we were late, You give us realization

01:22:18.303 --> 01:22:19.770
here."

01:22:19.795 --> 01:22:20.770
I said: "All right, have it."

01:22:21.522 --> 01:22:26.726
They had it, they are the ones who'll get
much faster than anyone else, I know, that's

01:22:26.751 --> 01:22:28.921
why I don't mind spending some time here.

01:22:28.946 --> 01:22:34.366
Once I go there, you will see the whole country
would be ablaze, I'm not telling you lies,

01:22:34.391 --> 01:22:36.314
you ask the people who have been there.

01:22:36.339 --> 01:22:41.439
They are very different type of people, to
them most important is their spirit.

01:22:41.464 --> 01:22:48.944
If you tell them what, the way we talk about
Christ here, so disrespectfully, without understanding,

01:22:48.969 --> 01:22:50.678
they are shocked.

01:22:50.737 --> 01:22:56.316
Any Indian who is a Christian or a Muslim
or a Hindu, doesn't treat the way you treat

01:22:56.341 --> 01:22:57.341
Bible.

01:22:58.855 --> 01:23:02.959
The respect they have has come to them traditionally.

01:23:03.134 --> 01:23:06.224
Of course you don't judge Indians by the Indians
who have come here.

01:23:06.224 --> 01:23:13.034
They like your company, they are this type,
they are materialistic, they want to have

01:23:13.034 --> 01:23:20.824
money, they have come here to earn money,
but the people who are in India in the villages,

01:23:20.824 --> 01:23:29.064
not in the cities, are still seeking, seeking
God, they're very simple people, humble people.

01:23:29.064 --> 01:23:31.514
Traditionally we have known for thousands
of years.

01:23:31.514 --> 01:23:40.265
I talk of Markandeya who was there twelve
thousand years back, who incarnated here as

01:23:40.265 --> 01:23:42.075
William Blake.

01:23:42.639 --> 01:23:47.314
Twelve thousand years back He said the same
thing which is said in England after twelve

01:23:47.314 --> 01:23:51.042
thousand years, because that time I don't
know what was here, may be only jungles, I

01:23:51.067 --> 01:23:52.217
think.

01:23:54.684 --> 01:24:01.944
And that is also waste, isn't it, tell Me,
isn't it?

01:24:01.944 --> 01:24:04.584
How much could Christ talk about kundalini?

01:24:04.584 --> 01:24:07.734
He talked of Holy Ghost.

01:24:07.734 --> 01:24:14.237
But why stick on to that, now I have come
to talk to you.

01:24:14.237 --> 01:24:19.645
Better take your realization; when He came,
they talked of Moses, when Moses came they

01:24:19.645 --> 01:24:20.645
talked of Abraham.

01:24:20.645 --> 01:24:29.574
What about the present, I am with you, why
not have your realization?

01:24:29.574 --> 01:24:34.814
All religions were built for this day, that
you get your realization, to give you the

01:24:34.814 --> 01:24:40.704
balance, to give you that property by which
you ascend.

01:24:40.704 --> 01:24:45.064
Like when we have an aeroplane, we fix it
up properly; in the same way they wanted to

01:24:45.064 --> 01:24:51.574
fix you up, but the religions went astray,
they made people crooked, the things they

01:24:51.574 --> 01:24:56.274
fixed, wrong bolts into wrong places, the
whole aeroplane is in a tattered condition

01:24:56.274 --> 01:24:59.574
if it flies, it will all fall down.

01:24:59.574 --> 01:25:03.124
Better give up all those ideas.

01:25:03.124 --> 01:25:10.284
But kundalini is such a great force, it's
such a great force; it comforts you, it cures

01:25:10.284 --> 01:25:16.874
you, it builds up all your centers and slowly
moves upward and when if you get realization,

01:25:16.874 --> 01:25:20.378
also it goes back, attends to all these problems
that

01:25:20.410 --> 01:25:21.385
you have.

01:25:21.385 --> 01:25:26.485
It's such a mother she is.

01:25:26.485 --> 01:25:29.885
Any other question, please?

01:25:29.885 --> 01:25:34.235
Q. Why are you to be known as Mataji, Mother?

01:25:34.235 --> 01:25:37.445
Shri Mataji: I didn't follow.

01:25:37.445 --> 01:25:41.525
Yogi: Nor did I.

01:25:41.525 --> 01:25:44.955
Why are You to be known as Mataji?

01:25:44.955 --> 01:25:47.355
Shri Mataji: As Shri Mataji?

01:25:58.036 --> 01:26:01.846
That's the title they gave Me, what can I
do?

01:26:01.846 --> 01:26:08.596
In India.

01:26:08.596 --> 01:26:11.476
You have to be an Indian to understand that.

01:26:11.476 --> 01:26:18.956
There are certain things described, about
Shri Mataji.

01:26:18.956 --> 01:26:31.846
If you have read any books, of Adi Shankaracharya,
or of Markandeya Himself, then you will know

01:26:31.846 --> 01:26:40.746
and the qualities described there of such
a person, if they find it in someone, they

01:26:40.746 --> 01:26:45.236
call that person by that name, isn't it?

01:26:45.236 --> 01:26:49.796
Like Gandhiji was called as Mahatma Gandhi.

01:26:49.796 --> 01:26:57.086
Mahatma means a bigger spirit than others,
because he had that.

01:26:57.086 --> 01:27:02.816
He didn't care for himself or his own family,
everything for his own, but he thought of

01:27:02.816 --> 01:27:07.946
the whole country; that's why he was called
Mahatma.

01:27:07.946 --> 01:27:18.076
Now, but I didn't call Myself; if others want
to call I think is all right, I have no objection.

01:27:18.076 --> 01:27:23.736
You can call anything, whatever you see, you
can call that.

01:27:23.736 --> 01:27:29.016
By calling that, what is your objection?

01:27:29.016 --> 01:27:31.306
Can I ask you this question?

01:27:31.306 --> 01:27:32.746
Beg pardon?

01:27:32.746 --> 01:27:35.636
[No objection] No objection.

01:27:35.636 --> 01:27:39.256
All right, that's all right.

01:27:39.256 --> 01:27:48.506
See, then it's all right, if you understand
that it is must be some reason also.

01:27:48.506 --> 01:27:52.106
(Further question from same person)

01:27:52.106 --> 01:27:54.816
Q. Do you have some divine power?

01:27:54.816 --> 01:28:00.976
Shri Mataji: That you better find out; I am
not going to be tactless on that.

01:28:00.976 --> 01:28:09.236
Christ said what was the truth, that He was
the Son of God, all right, but they crucified

01:28:09.236 --> 01:28:10.886
Him.

01:28:10.886 --> 01:28:20.556
I don't want to get crucified so soon.

01:28:20.556 --> 01:28:30.956
[INAUDIBLE Q:] But the one who is an Indian,
who is an Indian and Englishman.

01:28:30.956 --> 01:28:33.816
[Hindi].

01:28:33.816 --> 01:28:55.316
You see
it is for an ... Indians understand it better.

01:28:55.316 --> 01:29:10.376
[Hindi]
I'm sorry I'm speaking in Hindi because I

01:29:10.376 --> 01:29:26.446
have to little bit chastise the Indians here,
I hope you don't mind.

01:29:26.446 --> 01:29:27.746
[Hindi]

01:30:30.415 --> 01:30:33.415
Now, what is another question please?

01:30:34.431 --> 01:30:35.700
Yes please?

01:30:35.977 --> 01:30:37.124
Q. Yogi: Mother, she is
900
01:32:18,283 --&gt; 01:30:49,310
asking if you can cure physical ailment, I
mean the answer's yes, that comes from Self-realization,

01:30:49.310 --> 01:30:51.003
no question.

01:30:51.028 --> 01:30:57.064
Shri Mataji with your permission, the majority
of people have come for the experience and

01:30:57.170 --> 01:31:04.222
are anxious to have, I may be mistaken, but
I think most people would like to stop questions

01:31:04.247 --> 01:31:04.833
and ...

01:31:04.858 --> 01:31:07.389
Shri Mataji: But sometimes you know those
who want to ask, let them ask, otherwise the

01:31:07.414 --> 01:31:09.225
brain will again put out a question.

01:31:09.250 --> 01:31:13.510
Now madam, what is it..?

01:31:16.115 --> 01:31:17.115
(SY.

01:31:17.140 --> 01:31:19.855
She's asking You, Mother, what life was like
for You as a child)?

01:31:19.880 --> 01:31:21.593
Shri Mataji: As a child?

01:31:21.618 --> 01:31:26.548
I mean that's another story; you come and
see Me, I'll tell you all about it.

01:31:29.050 --> 01:31:35.800
Why do you want to know about My past and
future?

01:31:35.800 --> 01:31:42.560
Let us at the present time to get your realization;
makes no difference what I was as a child,

01:31:42.560 --> 01:31:45.850
or what I was as an old woman.

01:31:45.850 --> 01:32:00.080
Yogi: ... She's asking whether you have an
opinion about the growth of interest in spirituality

01:32:00.080 --> 01:32:01.080
in England...

01:32:01.080 --> 01:32:02.920
Shri Mataji: What spirituality?

01:32:02.920 --> 01:32:05.750
Yogi asks questioner: spiritualism or spirituality?

01:32:05.750 --> 01:32:07.170
Questioner answers: spiritualism.

01:32:07.170 --> 01:32:11.600
Shri Mataji: That's the witchcraft, revived;
very, very dangerous.

01:32:11.600 --> 01:32:19.930
Ah, is very dangerous, never go near that,
all this parapsychology and all those things.

01:32:19.930 --> 01:32:23.060
We have described all these things in our
book; you can have a look at it.

01:32:23.060 --> 01:32:25.380
Is a very comprehensive thing, Sahaja Yoga
is.

01:32:25.380 --> 01:32:30.570
Is the witchcraft, you may call it spirituality,
because a spirit can be also a dead soul as

01:32:30.570 --> 01:32:32.320
I told you, in English language.

01:32:32.320 --> 01:32:35.045
There is no 'ism' about God.

01:32:35.070 --> 01:32:37.589
It's infinite.

01:32:38.775 --> 01:32:49.690
'Isms' are all finite things.

01:32:49.690 --> 01:33:19.470
Q. SY: she's praising Your lecture, Mother,
and saying now that....she'll go back to read

01:33:19.470 --> 01:33:20.470
Blake again.

01:33:20.470 --> 01:33:23.310
Shri Mataji: I'm very happy, I'm very happy
that you say that, madam, it's really such

01:33:23.310 --> 01:33:27.860
a great poet, but you'll be surprised in India,
none of them brought Blake.

01:33:27.860 --> 01:33:33.370
We never read Blake there, never; you see
we studied English language, we studied Shakespeare,

01:33:33.370 --> 01:33:38.220
we studied so many things, but never they
mentioned Blake, you know.

01:33:38.220 --> 01:33:39.220
I don't know why.

01:33:39.220 --> 01:33:44.410
In the whole education system of India, they
never mentioned Blake.

01:33:44.410 --> 01:33:52.760
[another inaudible question ...]
Shri Mataji: That's very nice, such books

01:33:52.760 --> 01:33:53.820
you must read.

01:33:53.820 --> 01:34:00.070
Such books you must read.

01:34:00.070 --> 01:34:23.550
[Here someone disclaims in Sanskrit]
You see there's a Sanskrit scholar here, but

01:34:23.550 --> 01:34:27.250
the greatest Guru is the Mother, don't you
think so?

01:34:27.250 --> 01:34:31.921
The Mother is the Guru of the gurus.

01:34:31.946 --> 01:34:37.450
But it's very difficult, because guru is a
hard stuff, you see.

01:34:37.450 --> 01:34:44.410
A mother has to be very soft, kind, gentle
to manage the show, but the guru can be very

01:34:44.410 --> 01:34:56.523
hard and they are very hard people, but Mother
as a guru is a difficult task, it's very enjoyable.

