01:40:31.051 --> 01:40:36.691
Now we have to do is to ourselves awaken our
own kundalini, which is very simple, which

01:40:36.691 --> 01:40:38.021
I will tell you.

01:40:38.021 --> 01:40:43.651
In the heart resides the spirit so first we'll
have to put our hand to our heart.

01:40:43.651 --> 01:40:46.451
I will tell you one by one.

01:40:46.451 --> 01:40:51.282
And then in the upper part of your stomach
where the guru tattwa is here, the principle

01:40:51.282 --> 01:40:53.471
of guru is there.

01:40:53.471 --> 01:41:11.051
Then in the lower part of the abdomen, where
it is the divine, or we can say the pure knowledge

01:41:11.051 --> 01:41:13.801
that exists and which works.

01:41:13.801 --> 01:41:21.491
This is the center through which the pure
knowledge, the pure technique, works.

01:41:21.491 --> 01:41:36.401
Then we take this hand again back, same way,
up to this point where, it is here, when we

01:41:36.401 --> 01:41:40.901
are guilty we catch this chakra.

01:41:40.901 --> 01:41:48.111
Now here works our self-confidence, our faith
in God that He forgives us.

01:41:48.111 --> 01:41:56.461
Then we put our hand on top of our head - this
is the Agnya Chakra, which is very important.

01:41:56.461 --> 01:42:03.161
Here we forgive everyone; then at the back
of the Agnya Chakra again, where we have to

01:42:03.161 --> 01:42:06.971
say that, "If we done any mistake, oh God
forgive us".

01:42:06.971 --> 01:42:10.031
These are the two sides of the Agnya Chakra.

01:42:10.031 --> 01:42:17.331
And then you put your hand, stretch it, put
this part on the fontanel bone area, the soft

01:42:17.331 --> 01:42:25.971
bone which was on top of our head and press
it hard and move it hard, for a while.

01:42:25.971 --> 01:42:27.071
That's all one has to do.

01:42:27.071 --> 01:42:28.981
I'll tell you one by one.

01:42:28.981 --> 01:42:35.061
First and foremost thing is, we have to close
our eyes, because eyes take out our attention;

01:42:35.061 --> 01:42:42.051
but attention will be sucked inside our body
in the sense it will go through the - just

01:42:42.051 --> 01:42:47.661
like this cloth - it is spread out, but as
kundalini rises, She sucks it in and then

01:42:47.661 --> 01:42:55.071
pierces through this attention, enlight[en]ing
all of that.

01:42:55.071 --> 01:42:59.721
It's a happening that takes place without
any trouble whatsoever.

01:42:59.721 --> 01:43:08.011
As a result of that, what you get is the cool
breeze coming out of your head; you can also

01:43:08.011 --> 01:43:17.751
feel the cool breeze in your fingertips; then
later on in your hands and you get that shine

01:43:17.751 --> 01:43:19.801
on your skin.

01:43:19.801 --> 01:43:26.841
Christ has said, "The face that does not shine
cannot become the star."

01:43:26.841 --> 01:43:32.921
And then you get that glint of shine of the
spirit in your eyes.

01:43:32.921 --> 01:43:43.031
That's all, is not the point, is much, much,
