01:43:43.031 --> 01:43:49.691
have to today testify and later on to find
out have we got realization all right, then

01:43:49.691 --> 01:43:56.541
can we work it out, can we do this, because
later on we have to play our role now as a

01:43:56.541 --> 01:44:00.771
spiritual being, that's the point one has
to understand.

01:44:00.771 --> 01:44:09.211
So now, have respect for yourself first of
all; and not to feel guilty at all.

01:44:09.211 --> 01:44:16.871
You are the temple of God, really believe
Me you are made that way, only the light is

01:44:16.871 --> 01:44:20.391
to be kindled and that is in your heart.

01:44:20.391 --> 01:44:25.751
When the kundalini rises, she's something
like an energy that does that because when

01:44:25.751 --> 01:44:33.371
she pierces through, this is the place where
the God Almighty resides, who is reflected

01:44:33.371 --> 01:44:45.101
in our heart as the spirit and the all-pervading
power, which is the Primordial Mother, the

01:44:45.101 --> 01:44:53.062
Holy Ghost, this vibrations that you feel,
the power of God, the love of God which is

01:44:53.062 --> 01:45:03.231
represented within us as the kundalini, rises
and unites us, our attention to the Divine.

01:45:03.231 --> 01:45:12.371
The spirit enlightens the attention and by
that enlightenment you know, on your fingertips,

01:45:12.371 --> 01:45:18.511
on your central nervous system, through your
new collective consciousness about yourself

01:45:18.511 --> 01:45:19.781
and about others.

