01:45:44.061 --> 01:45:51.261
Without getting realization you can be happy
and unhappy but you cannot be joy, which has

01:45:51.261 --> 01:45:52.951
no dualism.

01:45:52.951 --> 01:45:55.341
You become the source of joy.

