01:48:32.231 --> 01:48:33.981
Just help Him out a little.

01:48:33.981 --> 01:48:34.981
All right.

01:48:34.981 --> 01:48:35.981
Let us see.

01:48:35.981 --> 01:48:41.631
So we put our both the hands like this, close
our eyes.

01:48:41.631 --> 01:48:47.921
Now you have to keep the left hand all the
time towards Me, because is the desire, is

01:48:47.921 --> 01:48:52.391
expressed through it is the power of desire
in the left hand which expresses that you

01:48:52.391 --> 01:48:53.521
want to have realization.

01:48:53.521 --> 01:48:58.941
The right hand is the power of action so you
move your right hand but don't open your eyes.

01:48:58.941 --> 01:49:06.371
You have to keep your eyes all the time shut,
just the opposite of mesmerism as you can

01:49:06.371 --> 01:49:07.491
see.

01:49:07.491 --> 01:49:26.431
Now please close your eyes; now put your right
hand on your heart.

01:49:26.431 --> 01:49:37.941
Now here you have to say, or ask Me a question,
"Mother am I the spirit?"

01:49:37.941 --> 01:49:41.451
You may call Me Shri Mataji or Mother, whatever
suits you.

01:49:41.451 --> 01:49:46.271
"Mother am I the spirit?" is a fundamental
question and if you are a computer it will

01:49:46.271 --> 01:49:47.271
answer.

01:49:47.271 --> 01:49:49.241
"Mother am I the spirit?"

01:49:49.241 --> 01:49:51.511
Ask the question three times please.

01:49:51.511 --> 01:50:01.971
Put your left hand properly, please close
your eyes; everybody should do it, please.

01:50:01.971 --> 01:50:09.831
It's uncivil not to close your eyes; please
close your eyes because others may feel self-conscious

01:50:09.831 --> 01:50:20.381
so please close your eyes, to be courteous.

01:50:20.381 --> 01:50:27.181
Now you have to take down your right hand
on the upper part of your stomach, on the

01:50:27.181 --> 01:50:31.231
left hand side, we are working only on the
left hand side.

01:50:31.231 --> 01:50:37.451
Here is the principle of the master.

01:50:37.451 --> 01:50:42.291
If you are the spirit, automatically you have
to ask the second question, "Mother am I my

01:50:42.291 --> 01:50:44.511
own master?

01:50:44.511 --> 01:50:46.641
Mother am I my own guru?"

01:50:46.641 --> 01:50:53.861
Please ask this question, you have to ask
this question three times again, without fear,

01:50:53.861 --> 01:51:09.091
with all confidence you ask this question,
you are the spirit, you are your master.

01:51:09.091 --> 01:51:18.591
Now move your right hand on the lower part
of your abdomen on the left hand side, lower

01:51:18.591 --> 01:51:20.931
part of your abdomen on the left hand side.

01:51:20.931 --> 01:51:30.731
This is the center of the divine work, of
the divine knowledge or the pure knowledge,

01:51:30.731 --> 01:51:35.481
of the technique of divine manifestation.

01:51:35.481 --> 01:51:45.282
At this point I cannot force you to do anything,
as I told you, you have to be free, I can

01:51:45.282 --> 01:51:52.121
only request you and here I say that you have
to ask for the divine knowledge, you have

01:51:52.121 --> 01:52:00.201
to ask for the pure knowledge and when you
ask for it the kundalini will start moving.

01:52:00.201 --> 01:52:08.881
Here with sincere heart, in a humble way you
have to say, "Mother may I have the pure knowledge,

01:52:08.881 --> 01:52:13.941
Mother may I have the divine technique?"

01:52:13.941 --> 01:52:38.141
Ask this question six times because this center
has got six petals.

01:52:38.141 --> 01:53:04.851
Now to make the way easy for kundalini, we
go along the same centers upwards so you put

01:53:04.851 --> 01:53:12.601
your right hand on the upper part of your
abdomen, to make it easy for the kundalini

01:53:12.601 --> 01:53:26.681
to rise you have to open this center by asserting,
by saying "Mother I am my own master", by

01:53:26.681 --> 01:53:52.151
saying "Mother I am my own master", ten times
because there are ten petals, ten Sat gurus

01:53:52.151 --> 01:54:24.391
basically who incarnate ten times, of Prophets,
the Masters.

01:54:24.391 --> 01:54:30.391
Now raise your right hand on your heart, press
it.

01:54:30.391 --> 01:54:44.051
With the same confidence you have to say twelve
times "Mother I am the spirit, I am the spirit,

01:54:44.051 --> 01:54:47.601
I am the spirit".

01:54:47.601 --> 01:55:04.081
Just assert, that's a fact, that's the truth.

01:55:04.081 --> 01:55:14.771
Press it with your fingers.

01:55:14.771 --> 01:55:26.411
Now, twelve times, have full confidence in
you, believe Me you are the spirit, you have

01:55:26.411 --> 01:55:32.301
to just become in the sense it has to come
in your attention on to your central nervous

01:55:32.301 --> 01:55:58.761
system.

01:55:58.761 --> 01:56:10.971
Now raise the right hand on the left hand
side of your neck, in the corner where the

01:56:10.971 --> 01:56:15.841
neck and the shoulder meet, press it hard,
take it backwards, press it hard.

01:56:15.841 --> 01:56:21.271
This is the most difficult center in the West,
as I told you, that we feel guilty all the

01:56:21.271 --> 01:56:32.231
time but as I have told you, God is the ocean
of love, ocean of compassion, but above all

01:56:32.231 --> 01:56:34.371
He is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:56:34.371 --> 01:56:38.031
He's the ocean of forgiveness.

01:56:38.031 --> 01:56:46.951
When He's the ocean of forgiveness, what guilt
can we have that He cannot wash away or dissolve

01:56:46.951 --> 01:56:47.951
it?

01:56:47.951 --> 01:56:55.051
So just you have to say sixteen times because
there are sixteen petals, to say sixteen times

01:56:55.051 --> 01:57:00.161
with full belief in yourself, "Mother I'm
not guilty, Mother, I'm not guilty, Mother,

01:57:00.161 --> 01:57:48.541
I'm not guilty" sixteen times will you please
say that "Shri Mataji I'm not guilty".

01:57:48.541 --> 01:57:53.381
If you still feel you are guilty and you can't
forgive yourself, better say it to punish

01:57:53.381 --> 01:58:09.771
yourself hundred and eight times, if that
pleases you.

01:58:09.771 --> 01:58:31.231
When you forgive yourself you have to forgive
others and so the greatest message of Christ,

01:58:31.231 --> 01:58:39.081
that we have to forgive others you have to
put your hand to the center which is the adornment

01:58:39.081 --> 01:58:46.721
or we should say which adorns Christ, on the
Agnya Chakra on your forehead, please put

01:58:46.721 --> 01:58:49.141
your right hand across,.

01:58:49.141 --> 01:59:05.491
Press it hard and here you have to say with
full belief in yourself and in your powers

01:59:05.491 --> 01:59:11.811
that, "Shri Mataji I forgive everyone".

01:59:11.811 --> 01:59:16.891
Some may say that's very difficult but what
do we do when we forgive or not forgive - no

01:59:16.891 --> 01:59:18.051
logic in it.

01:59:18.051 --> 01:59:28.081
But when we say that, then we are out of the
clutches of other people, so please say, "Shri

01:59:28.081 --> 01:59:30.931
Mataji I forgive everyone.

01:59:30.931 --> 01:59:50.701
Now say it with your whole heart, how many
times is not the point, please say it with

01:59:50.701 --> 01:59:51.701
your whole heart.

01:59:51.701 --> 01:59:56.701
Now you move your hand backwards onto the
back side of the same center - Agnya - press

01:59:56.701 --> 01:59:58.541
it hard.

01:59:58.541 --> 02:00:09.661
Now here, you have to say once only without
feeling guilty at all, without feeling no

02:00:09.661 --> 02:00:17.491
remorse, no condemnation, to God, one for
your satisfaction, "Oh Lord, if I have done

02:00:17.491 --> 02:00:26.081
anything wrong, please forgive me" but don't
feel guilty, that's very important.

02:00:26.081 --> 02:00:36.811
Even without saying He has forgiven you.

02:00:36.811 --> 02:00:39.021
Better.

02:00:39.021 --> 02:00:46.632
Now raise your right hand on top of your head,
stretch your ... stretch your palm, press

02:00:46.632 --> 02:00:55.741
it hard on the fontanel bone area, which was
the soft bone in your childhood, press it

02:00:55.741 --> 02:00:57.891
hard, move it seven times.

02:00:57.891 --> 02:01:02.451
Again here I cannot force anything on you.

02:01:02.451 --> 02:01:09.721
You have to say that you want your Self-realization
that, "Mother, please give us our realization.

02:01:09.721 --> 02:01:11.971
We want our Self-realization.

02:01:11.971 --> 02:01:20.361
Please give me my Self-realization" and press
it hard and move it seven times and say that.

02:01:20.361 --> 02:01:34.721
I'm sure it will work out.

02:01:34.721 --> 02:02:15.411
Now bring down your hand, slowly, and bend
your head a little bit and feel with your

02:02:15.411 --> 02:02:38.811
left hand if there's a cool breeze coming
out of your fontanel bone area.

02:02:38.811 --> 02:02:43.681
Try to bend your head a little, little bit
and about four inches above the head, bend

02:02:43.681 --> 02:02:48.101
it a little, that works out better sometimes.

02:02:48.101 --> 02:03:01.641
With your left hand, right hand towards Me
and with the left hand you see the breeze.

02:03:01.641 --> 02:03:06.331
Right hand towards Me and then with the left
hand you see, you can feel it better, with

02:03:06.331 --> 02:03:11.201
the left hand on top of your head; first with
the left hand.

02:03:11.201 --> 02:03:12.621
Aah.

02:03:12.621 --> 02:03:19.971
Now put the left hand towards Me and with
the right hand just see if it is blowing because

02:03:19.971 --> 02:03:22.071
it should come in both the hands.

02:03:22.071 --> 02:03:30.831
Open your eyes, open slowly and watch Me without
thinking.

02:03:30.831 --> 02:03:42.161
Let us see if you can do it - just without
thinking, just watch Me, without thinking.

02:03:42.161 --> 02:03:52.641
There's no thought in your mind, no thought.

02:03:52.641 --> 02:04:03.471
Now just put your hands like this, are you
feeling the cool breeze in the hand?

02:04:03.471 --> 02:04:09.461
Now put your hands up in the air, like this,
and in your heart ask a question, "Is this

02:04:09.461 --> 02:04:11.611
the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?"

02:04:11.611 --> 02:04:17.361
Ask the question, put it up nicely, ask the
question three times: "Is this the cool breeze

02:04:17.361 --> 02:04:19.051
of the Holy Ghost?

02:04:19.051 --> 02:04:21.961
Is this the brahma shakti?

02:04:21.961 --> 02:04:26.361
Is this the all-pervading power of God?

02:04:26.361 --> 02:04:31.101
Ask the question.

02:04:31.101 --> 02:04:39.691
Now put down your hands and see for yourself
if you feel the cool breeze.

02:04:39.691 --> 02:04:50.201
All those who have felt the cool breeze on
the head, coming out of the head, or on their

02:04:50.201 --> 02:05:00.911
fingertips or in the hands please raise your
hands, both the hands.

02:05:00.911 --> 02:05:01.911
That's Blake.

02:05:01.911 --> 02:05:03.391
You all have become Blake.

02:05:03.391 --> 02:05:07.221
May God bless you.

02:05:07.221 --> 02:05:08.541
So many.

02:05:08.541 --> 02:05:09.701
May God bless you.

02:05:09.701 --> 02:05:15.611
But I must warn you, after this don't talk
about it because it is beyond reasoning.

02:05:15.611 --> 02:05:22.061
Secondly you must come back, must all of you
come back and work it out.

02:05:22.061 --> 02:05:27.351
Those who haven't got realization will also
receive it.

02:05:27.351 --> 02:05:30.571
Those who have got it, will establish it.

02:05:30.571 --> 02:05:31.961
Please come back.

02:05:31.961 --> 02:05:40.161
You will enjoy the silence, the stillness
within.

02:05:40.161 --> 02:05:42.961
But that's just the beginning of it.

02:05:42.961 --> 02:05:45.221
We have to go further.

02:05:45.221 --> 02:05:50.221
Otherwise you won't be able to manifest it
properly.

02:05:50.221 --> 02:05:51.801
It has to be looked after.

02:05:51.801 --> 02:06:01.458
It's just a shoot that has come out, a little
shoot we have to look after it.

02:06:01.483 --> 02:06:04.483
May God bless you all.

02:06:04.588 --> 02:06:09.818
Thank-you very much.

